      <title>法院否决 Signa 债务计划，称其“显然不可行”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/court-nixes-signa-debt-plan-saying-it-s-obviously-not-feasible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利法院阻止了 Signa Prime Selection AG 的重组尝试，称由债权人支持的出售 Rene Benko 旗舰子公司所持有的财产的计划“显然不可行”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/court-nixes-signa-debt-plan-saying-it-s-obviously-not-feasible</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风带来降雨，玉米、大豆价格跌至 2020 年以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/corn-slumps-to-lowest-since-2020-on-midwest-rain-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于飓风贝丽尔给中西部带来降雨，玉米和大豆价格跌至疫情高峰以来的最低水平，有可能在农作物生长的关键时期提高产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/corn-slumps-to-lowest-since-2020-on-midwest-rain-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，股市回调 10% 的可能性“非常大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-a-10-correction-is-highly-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利的迈克·威尔逊表示，由于美国总统竞选、企业盈利和美联储政策的不确定性加剧，交易员应为股市大幅回调做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-a-10-correction-is-highly-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币的 Mt. Gox 波动进一步表明加密货币反弹艰难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/bitcoin-btc-drops-anew-on-fears-of-sales-from-mt-gox-distributions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心破产的 Mt. Gox 交易所的债权人可能抛售比特币，比特币价格再次下跌，这加剧了人们对始于去年的加密货币牛市是否还能保持动力的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/bitcoin-btc-drops-anew-on-fears-of-sales-from-mt-gox-distributions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 01:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
